17static INLINE void vp8_loop_filter_neon(uint8x16_t qblimit, // flimit
18 uint8x16_t qlimit, // limit
19 uint8x16_t qthresh, // thresh
20 uint8x16_t q3, // p3
21 uint8x16_t q4, // p2
22 uint8x16_t q5, // p1
23 uint8x16_t q6, // p0
24 uint8x16_t q7, // q0
25 uint8x16_t q8, // q1
26 uint8x16_t q9, // q2
27 uint8x16_t q10, // q3
28 uint8x16_t *q5r, // p1
29 uint8x16_t *q6r, // p0
30 uint8x16_t *q7r, // q0
31 uint8x16_t *q8r) { // q1
32 uint8x16_t q0u8, q1u8, q2u8, q11u8, q12u8, q13u8, q14u8, q15u8;
33 int16x8_t q2s16, q11s16;
34 uint16x8_t q4u16;
35 int8x16_t q1s8, q2s8, q10s8, q11s8, q12s8, q13s8;
36 int8x8_t d2s8, d3s8;
37
38 q11u8 = vabdq_u8(q3, q4);
39 q12u8 = vabdq_u8(q4, q5);
40 q13u8 = vabdq_u8(q5, q6);
41 q14u8 = vabdq_u8(q8, q7);
42 q3 = vabdq_u8(q9, q8);
43 q4 = vabdq_u8(q10, q9);
44
45 q11u8 = vmaxq_u8(q11u8, q12u8);
46 q12u8 = vmaxq_u8(q13u8, q14u8);
47 q3 = vmaxq_u8(q3, q4);
48 q15u8 = vmaxq_u8(q11u8, q12u8);
49
50 q9 = vabdq_u8(q6, q7);
51
52 // vp8_hevmask
53 q13u8 = vcgtq_u8(q13u8, qthresh);
54 q14u8 = vcgtq_u8(q14u8, qthresh);
55 q15u8 = vmaxq_u8(q15u8, q3);
56
57 q2u8 = vabdq_u8(q5, q8);
58 q9 = vqaddq_u8(q9, q9);
59
60 q15u8 = vcgeq_u8(qlimit, q15u8);
61
62 // vp8_filter() function
63 // convert to signed
64 q10 = vdupq_n_u8(0x80);
65 q8 = veorq_u8(q8, q10);
66 q7 = veorq_u8(q7, q10);
67 q6 = veorq_u8(q6, q10);
68 q5 = veorq_u8(q5, q10);
69
70 q2u8 = vshrq_n_u8(q2u8, 1);
71 q9 = vqaddq_u8(q9, q2u8);
72
73 q10 = vdupq_n_u8(3);
74
75 q2s16 = vsubl_s8(vget_low_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q7)),
76 vget_low_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q6)));
77 q11s16 = vsubl_s8(vget_high_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q7)),
78 vget_high_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q6)));
79
80 q9 = vcgeq_u8(qblimit, q9);
81
82 q1s8 = vqsubq_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q5), vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q8));
83
84 q14u8 = vorrq_u8(q13u8, q14u8);
85
86 q4u16 = vmovl_u8(vget_low_u8(q10));
87 q2s16 = vmulq_s16(q2s16, vreinterpretq_s16_u16(q4u16));
88 q11s16 = vmulq_s16(q11s16, vreinterpretq_s16_u16(q4u16));
89
90 q1u8 = vandq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q1s8), q14u8);
91 q15u8 = vandq_u8(q15u8, q9);
92
93 q1s8 = vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q1u8);
94 q2s16 = vaddw_s8(q2s16, vget_low_s8(q1s8));
95 q11s16 = vaddw_s8(q11s16, vget_high_s8(q1s8));
96
97 q9 = vdupq_n_u8(4);
98 // vp8_filter = clamp(vp8_filter + 3 * ( qs0 - ps0))
99 d2s8 = vqmovn_s16(q2s16);
100 d3s8 = vqmovn_s16(q11s16);
101 q1s8 = vcombine_s8(d2s8, d3s8);
102 q1u8 = vandq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q1s8), q15u8);
103 q1s8 = vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q1u8);
104
105 q2s8 = vqaddq_s8(q1s8, vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q10));
106 q1s8 = vqaddq_s8(q1s8, vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q9));
107 q2s8 = vshrq_n_s8(q2s8, 3);
108 q1s8 = vshrq_n_s8(q1s8, 3);
109
110 q11s8 = vqaddq_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q6), q2s8);
111 q10s8 = vqsubq_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q7), q1s8);
112
113 q1s8 = vrshrq_n_s8(q1s8, 1);
114 q1s8 = vbicq_s8(q1s8, vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q14u8));
115
116 q13s8 = vqaddq_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q5), q1s8);
117 q12s8 = vqsubq_s8(vreinterpretq_s8_u8(q8), q1s8);
118
119 q0u8 = vdupq_n_u8(0x80);
120 *q8r = veorq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q12s8), q0u8);
121 *q7r = veorq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q10s8), q0u8);
122 *q6r = veorq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q11s8), q0u8);
123 *q5r = veorq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_s8(q13s8), q0u8);
124 return;
125}

127void vp8_loop_filter_horizontal_edge_y_neon(unsigned char *src, int pitch,
128 unsigned char blimit,
129 unsigned char limit,
130 unsigned char thresh) {
131 uint8x16_t qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4;
132 uint8x16_t q5, q6, q7, q8, q9, q10;
133
134 qblimit = vdupq_n_u8(blimit);
135 qlimit = vdupq_n_u8(limit);
136 qthresh = vdupq_n_u8(thresh);
137 src -= (pitch << 2);
138
139 q3 = vld1q_u8(src);
140 src += pitch;
141 q4 = vld1q_u8(src);
142 src += pitch;
143 q5 = vld1q_u8(src);
144 src += pitch;
145 q6 = vld1q_u8(src);
146 src += pitch;
147 q7 = vld1q_u8(src);
148 src += pitch;
149 q8 = vld1q_u8(src);
150 src += pitch;
151 q9 = vld1q_u8(src);
152 src += pitch;
153 q10 = vld1q_u8(src);
154
155 vp8_loop_filter_neon(qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4, q5, q6, q7, q8, q9,
156 q10, &q5, &q6, &q7, &q8);
157
158 src -= (pitch * 5);
159 vst1q_u8(src, q5);
160 src += pitch;
161 vst1q_u8(src, q6);
162 src += pitch;
163 vst1q_u8(src, q7);
164 src += pitch;
165 vst1q_u8(src, q8);
166 return;
167}

169void vp8_loop_filter_horizontal_edge_uv_neon(unsigned char *u, int pitch,
170 unsigned char blimit,
171 unsigned char limit,
172 unsigned char thresh,
173 unsigned char *v) {
174 uint8x16_t qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4;
175 uint8x16_t q5, q6, q7, q8, q9, q10;
176 uint8x8_t d6, d7, d8, d9, d10, d11, d12, d13, d14;
177 uint8x8_t d15, d16, d17, d18, d19, d20, d21;
178
179 qblimit = vdupq_n_u8(blimit);
180 qlimit = vdupq_n_u8(limit);
181 qthresh = vdupq_n_u8(thresh);
182
183 u -= (pitch << 2);
184 v -= (pitch << 2);
185
186 d6 = vld1_u8(u);
187 u += pitch;
188 d7 = vld1_u8(v);
189 v += pitch;
190 d8 = vld1_u8(u);
191 u += pitch;
192 d9 = vld1_u8(v);
193 v += pitch;
194 d10 = vld1_u8(u);
195 u += pitch;
196 d11 = vld1_u8(v);
197 v += pitch;
198 d12 = vld1_u8(u);
199 u += pitch;
200 d13 = vld1_u8(v);
201 v += pitch;
202 d14 = vld1_u8(u);
203 u += pitch;
204 d15 = vld1_u8(v);
205 v += pitch;
206 d16 = vld1_u8(u);
207 u += pitch;
208 d17 = vld1_u8(v);
209 v += pitch;
210 d18 = vld1_u8(u);
211 u += pitch;
212 d19 = vld1_u8(v);
213 v += pitch;
214 d20 = vld1_u8(u);
215 d21 = vld1_u8(v);
216
217 q3 = vcombine_u8(d6, d7);
218 q4 = vcombine_u8(d8, d9);
219 q5 = vcombine_u8(d10, d11);
220 q6 = vcombine_u8(d12, d13);
221 q7 = vcombine_u8(d14, d15);
222 q8 = vcombine_u8(d16, d17);
223 q9 = vcombine_u8(d18, d19);
224 q10 = vcombine_u8(d20, d21);
225
226 vp8_loop_filter_neon(qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4, q5, q6, q7, q8, q9,
227 q10, &q5, &q6, &q7, &q8);
228
229 u -= (pitch * 5);
230 vst1_u8(u, vget_low_u8(q5));
231 u += pitch;
232 vst1_u8(u, vget_low_u8(q6));
233 u += pitch;
234 vst1_u8(u, vget_low_u8(q7));
235 u += pitch;
236 vst1_u8(u, vget_low_u8(q8));
237
238 v -= (pitch * 5);
239 vst1_u8(v, vget_high_u8(q5));
240 v += pitch;
241 vst1_u8(v, vget_high_u8(q6));
242 v += pitch;
243 vst1_u8(v, vget_high_u8(q7));
244 v += pitch;
245 vst1_u8(v, vget_high_u8(q8));
246 return;
247}

249static INLINE void write_4x8(unsigned char *dst, int pitch,
250 const uint8x8x4_t result) {
251#ifdef VPX_INCOMPATIBLE_GCC
252 /*
253 * uint8x8x4_t result
254 00 01 02 03 | 04 05 06 07
255 10 11 12 13 | 14 15 16 17
256 20 21 22 23 | 24 25 26 27
257 30 31 32 33 | 34 35 36 37
258 ---
259 * after vtrn_u16
260 00 01 20 21 | 04 05 24 25
261 02 03 22 23 | 06 07 26 27
262 10 11 30 31 | 14 15 34 35
263 12 13 32 33 | 16 17 36 37
264 ---
265 * after vtrn_u8
266 00 10 20 30 | 04 14 24 34
267 01 11 21 31 | 05 15 25 35
268 02 12 22 32 | 06 16 26 36
269 03 13 23 33 | 07 17 27 37
270 */
271 const uint16x4x2_t r02_u16 = vtrn_u16(vreinterpret_u16_u8(result.val[0]),
272 vreinterpret_u16_u8(result.val[2]));
273 const uint16x4x2_t r13_u16 = vtrn_u16(vreinterpret_u16_u8(result.val[1]),
274 vreinterpret_u16_u8(result.val[3]));
275 const uint8x8x2_t r01_u8 = vtrn_u8(vreinterpret_u8_u16(r02_u16.val[0]),
276 vreinterpret_u8_u16(r13_u16.val[0]));
277 const uint8x8x2_t r23_u8 = vtrn_u8(vreinterpret_u8_u16(r02_u16.val[1]),
278 vreinterpret_u8_u16(r13_u16.val[1]));
279 const uint32x2_t x_0_4 = vreinterpret_u32_u8(r01_u8.val[0]);
280 const uint32x2_t x_1_5 = vreinterpret_u32_u8(r01_u8.val[1]);
281 const uint32x2_t x_2_6 = vreinterpret_u32_u8(r23_u8.val[0]);
282 const uint32x2_t x_3_7 = vreinterpret_u32_u8(r23_u8.val[1]);
283 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_0_4, 0);
284 dst += pitch;
285 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_1_5, 0);
286 dst += pitch;
287 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_2_6, 0);
288 dst += pitch;
289 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_3_7, 0);
290 dst += pitch;
291 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_0_4, 1);
292 dst += pitch;
293 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_1_5, 1);
294 dst += pitch;
295 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_2_6, 1);
296 dst += pitch;
297 vst1_lane_u32((uint32_t *)dst, x_3_7, 1);
298#else
299 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 0);
300 dst += pitch;
301 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 1);
302 dst += pitch;
303 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 2);
304 dst += pitch;
305 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 3);
306 dst += pitch;
307 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 4);
308 dst += pitch;
309 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 5);
310 dst += pitch;
311 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 6);
312 dst += pitch;
313 vst4_lane_u8(dst, result, 7);
314#endif // VPX_INCOMPATIBLE_GCC
315}

317void vp8_loop_filter_vertical_edge_y_neon(unsigned char *src, int pitch,
318 unsigned char blimit,
319 unsigned char limit,
320 unsigned char thresh) {
321 unsigned char *s, *d;
322 uint8x16_t qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4;
323 uint8x16_t q5, q6, q7, q8, q9, q10;
324 uint8x8_t d6, d7, d8, d9, d10, d11, d12, d13, d14;
325 uint8x8_t d15, d16, d17, d18, d19, d20, d21;
326 uint32x4x2_t q2tmp0, q2tmp1, q2tmp2, q2tmp3;
327 uint16x8x2_t q2tmp4, q2tmp5, q2tmp6, q2tmp7;
328 uint8x16x2_t q2tmp8, q2tmp9, q2tmp10, q2tmp11;
329 uint8x8x4_t q4ResultH, q4ResultL;
330
331 qblimit = vdupq_n_u8(blimit);
332 qlimit = vdupq_n_u8(limit);
333 qthresh = vdupq_n_u8(thresh);
334
335 s = src - 4;
336 d6 = vld1_u8(s);
337 s += pitch;
338 d8 = vld1_u8(s);
339 s += pitch;
340 d10 = vld1_u8(s);
341 s += pitch;
342 d12 = vld1_u8(s);
343 s += pitch;
344 d14 = vld1_u8(s);
345 s += pitch;
346 d16 = vld1_u8(s);
347 s += pitch;
348 d18 = vld1_u8(s);
349 s += pitch;
350 d20 = vld1_u8(s);
351 s += pitch;
352 d7 = vld1_u8(s);
353 s += pitch;
354 d9 = vld1_u8(s);
355 s += pitch;
356 d11 = vld1_u8(s);
357 s += pitch;
358 d13 = vld1_u8(s);
359 s += pitch;
360 d15 = vld1_u8(s);
361 s += pitch;
362 d17 = vld1_u8(s);
363 s += pitch;
364 d19 = vld1_u8(s);
365 s += pitch;
366 d21 = vld1_u8(s);
367
368 q3 = vcombine_u8(d6, d7);
369 q4 = vcombine_u8(d8, d9);
370 q5 = vcombine_u8(d10, d11);
371 q6 = vcombine_u8(d12, d13);
372 q7 = vcombine_u8(d14, d15);
373 q8 = vcombine_u8(d16, d17);
374 q9 = vcombine_u8(d18, d19);
375 q10 = vcombine_u8(d20, d21);
376
377 q2tmp0 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q3), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q7));
378 q2tmp1 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q4), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q8));
379 q2tmp2 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q5), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q9));
380 q2tmp3 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q6), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q10));
381
382 q2tmp4 = vtrnq_u16(vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp0.val[0]),
383 vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp2.val[0]));
384 q2tmp5 = vtrnq_u16(vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp1.val[0]),
385 vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp3.val[0]));
386 q2tmp6 = vtrnq_u16(vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp0.val[1]),
387 vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp2.val[1]));
388 q2tmp7 = vtrnq_u16(vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp1.val[1]),
389 vreinterpretq_u16_u32(q2tmp3.val[1]));
390
391 q2tmp8 = vtrnq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp4.val[0]),
392 vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp5.val[0]));
393 q2tmp9 = vtrnq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp4.val[1]),
394 vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp5.val[1]));
395 q2tmp10 = vtrnq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp6.val[0]),
396 vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp7.val[0]));
397 q2tmp11 = vtrnq_u8(vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp6.val[1]),
398 vreinterpretq_u8_u16(q2tmp7.val[1]));
399
400 q3 = q2tmp8.val[0];
401 q4 = q2tmp8.val[1];
402 q5 = q2tmp9.val[0];
403 q6 = q2tmp9.val[1];
404 q7 = q2tmp10.val[0];
405 q8 = q2tmp10.val[1];
406 q9 = q2tmp11.val[0];
407 q10 = q2tmp11.val[1];
408
409 vp8_loop_filter_neon(qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4, q5, q6, q7, q8, q9,
410 q10, &q5, &q6, &q7, &q8);
411
412 q4ResultL.val[0] = vget_low_u8(q5); // d10
413 q4ResultL.val[1] = vget_low_u8(q6); // d12
414 q4ResultL.val[2] = vget_low_u8(q7); // d14
415 q4ResultL.val[3] = vget_low_u8(q8); // d16
416 q4ResultH.val[0] = vget_high_u8(q5); // d11
417 q4ResultH.val[1] = vget_high_u8(q6); // d13
418 q4ResultH.val[2] = vget_high_u8(q7); // d15
419 q4ResultH.val[3] = vget_high_u8(q8); // d17
420
421 d = src - 2;
422 write_4x8(d, pitch, q4ResultL);
423 d += pitch * 8;
424 write_4x8(d, pitch, q4ResultH);
425}

427void vp8_loop_filter_vertical_edge_uv_neon(unsigned char *u, int pitch,
428 unsigned char blimit,
429 unsigned char limit,
430 unsigned char thresh,
431 unsigned char *v) {
432 unsigned char *us, *ud;
433 unsigned char *vs, *vd;
434 uint8x16_t qblimit, qlimit, qthresh, q3, q4;
435 uint8x16_t q5, q6, q7, q8, q9, q10;
436 uint8x8_t d6, d7, d8, d9, d10, d11, d12, d13, d14;
437 uint8x8_t d15, d16, d17, d18, d19, d20, d21;
438 uint32x4x2_t q2tmp0, q2tmp1, q2tmp2, q2tmp3;
439 uint16x8x2_t q2tmp4, q2tmp5, q2tmp6, q2tmp7;
440 uint8x16x2_t q2tmp8, q2tmp9, q2tmp10, q2tmp11;
441 uint8x8x4_t q4ResultH, q4ResultL;
442
443 qblimit = vdupq_n_u8(blimit);
444 qlimit = vdupq_n_u8(limit);
445 qthresh = vdupq_n_u8(thresh);
446
447 us = u - 4;
448 d6 = vld1_u8(us);
449 us += pitch;
450 d8 = vld1_u8(us);
451 us += pitch;
452 d10 = vld1_u8(us);
453 us += pitch;
454 d12 = vld1_u8(us);
455 us += pitch;
456 d14 = vld1_u8(us);
457 us += pitch;
458 d16 = vld1_u8(us);
459 us += pitch;
460 d18 = vld1_u8(us);
461 us += pitch;
462 d20 = vld1_u8(us);
463
464 vs = v - 4;
465 d7 = vld1_u8(vs);
466 vs += pitch;
467 d9 = vld1_u8(vs);
468 vs += pitch;
469 d11 = vld1_u8(vs);
470 vs += pitch;
471 d13 = vld1_u8(vs);
472 vs += pitch;
473 d15 = vld1_u8(vs);
474 vs += pitch;
475 d17 = vld1_u8(vs);
476 vs += pitch;
477 d19 = vld1_u8(vs);
478 vs += pitch;
479 d21 = vld1_u8(vs);
480
481 q3 = vcombine_u8(d6, d7);
482 q4 = vcombine_u8(d8, d9);
483 q5 = vcombine_u8(d10, d11);
484 q6 = vcombine_u8(d12, d13);
485 q7 = vcombine_u8(d14, d15);
486 q8 = vcombine_u8(d16, d17);
487 q9 = vcombine_u8(d18, d19);
488 q10 = vcombine_u8(d20, d21);
489
490 q2tmp0 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q3), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q7));
491 q2tmp1 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q4), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q8));
492 q2tmp2 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q5), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q9));
493 q2tmp3 = vtrnq_u32(vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q6), vreinterpretq_u32_u8(q10));
494
